translation[8]{c,v,t}:
  2,62,Ngempela labo abakholwayo nalabo ababengamaJuda namaKrestu namaSabiya noma ngabe ngubani owakholelwa kuMvelinqangi nososukwini lokugcina wenza okuhle umvuzo wakhe useNkosini yakhe abayukwesaba futhi angeke bakhathazeke
  2,63,"Futhi (khumbulani) ngesikathi senza isivumelwano nani (bantwana bakwa Israyeli) senza intaba iSinayi yaba umqongo ngaphezu kwenu kwathiwa thathani ngeqiniso lokho esaninika kona, nikhumbule okuqukethwe yiko ngaphakathi ukuze nibe ngabalungileyo"
  2,64,Nabe seniyaphenduka (naphambuka) emuva kwalokho uma babungekho ububele buka-Mvelinqangi phezu kwenu nomusa wakhe naniyoba kanye nalabo abalahlekelweyo
  2,65,"Futhi nivele niyabazi kahle labo kunina abephula (umthetho) weSabatha, futhi sathi kubona “yibani yizinkawu ezilahliweyo”"
  2,66,Sakwenza lokho kwaba yisijeziso kulabo ababekhona nasezizukulwaneni zabo futhi kuyisifundo kulabo abesaba (uMvelinqangi)
  2,67,"Futhi khumbulani ngesikhathi uMose ethi kubantu bakhe, “ngempela uMvelinqangi uniyalela ukuba nihlabe inkomo (umnikelo ngenkomo), bathi “ngakube usithathisa okweziwula na?” wathi, “Oh! Mvelinqangi! Ngicela isiphephelo (kuwena) ukuze ngingabi kanye nalabo abangazi lutho”"
  2,68,"Bathi (abantwana bakwa-Israyeli) “tshena iNkosi yakho isicacisele ukuthi inkomoni leyo” wathi (uMose), “ngempela yena (uMvelinqangi) uthi kufanele kube yinkomo engeyindala futhi engeyincane mayibe phakathi kwalokho”, yenzani lokho eniyalelwe ngakho"
  2,69,"Bathi, “sitshelele iNkosi yakho isicacisele ukuthi imubala njani na? Wathi (uMose) ngempela yena uthi “Iyinkomo encombo enombala ogqamile encomekayo kwabayibonayo”"